description:
branch: MASTER

In case of --instance_name_template flag usage, the new image cache manager will failed on listing the backing images currently in use.

=> hence used images can be deleted.

in the following code from (nova/virt/libvirt/imagecache.py:L120):

def _list_backing_images(self):
        """List the backing images currently in use."""
        inuse_images = []
        for ent in os.listdir(FLAGS.instances_path):
            if ent.startswith('instance-'):

FLAGS.instance_name_template must be used instead of using ent.startswith('instance-')

